    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Burning Hands</strong> (Level 1 Evocation)</p><p>As you hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread, a thin sheet of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips. Each creature in a 15-foot cone must make a dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>The fire ignites any flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Self | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
